description: Cold-weather days call for reliable protection. The Men’s Alpine Polartec™ 200 Full-Zip Hooded Jacket has a flexible four-way stretch, hem and hood adjustability and a water-repellent overlay. As one of our Circular Design styles, it’s made with sustainably-conscious materials and recyclable when you get it back to us.
name: The North Face Alpine Polartec 200 Full Zip Jacket - Mens
